    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are explicitly scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 guidance for Class II devices at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1 at all five operating points with NIH predictions within 14.3% of experimental means. The UQ campaign documented in the validation report confirms robustness of hemolysis predictions across the uncertainty space. The computational model is assessed as sufficiently credible for the stated CPB COU.",
